l've arranged a place foryou

359
00:30:51,397 --> 00:30:53,353  X1:296 X2:402 Y1:474 Y2:500
Thank you

360
00:30:54,437 --> 00:30:55,586  X1:281 X2:419 Y1:474 Y2:495
Do remember

361
00:30:56,477 --> 00:30:58,752  X1:174 X2:524 Y1:474 Y2:500
l'm not one of those you've helped

362
00:31:03,717 --> 00:31:05,594  X1:223 X2:475 Y1:474 Y2:500
Of all the people l've met

363
00:31:05,797 --> 00:31:09,028  X1:214 X2:484 Y1:474 Y2:500
you're one of the toughest

364
00:31:33,517 --> 00:31:35,712  X1:250 X2:448 Y1:474 Y2:500
ls Miss Wang here?

365
00:31:51,305 --> 00:31:55,298  X1:164 X2:533 Y1:474 Y2:495
When was the last time Li was here?

366
00:31:56,705 --> 00:31:58,980  X1:215 X2:484 Y1:474 Y2:500
More than two months ago

367
00:31:59,545 --> 00:32:01,661  X1:228 X2:470 Y1:474 Y2:500
How many days is that?

368
00:32:03,065 --> 00:32:05,420  X1:171 X2:528 Y1:474 Y2:500
Sixty eight days ago in the evening

369
00:32:05,705 --> 00:32:07,775  X1:188 X2:510 Y1:474 Y2:495
That was the last time l saw him

370
00:32:10,305 --> 00:32:12,500  X1:273 X2:426 Y1:474 Y2:495
That was exact

371
00:32:13,105 --> 00:32:16,700  X1:172 X2:526 Y1:474 Y2:500
You really don't know where he is?

372
00:32:18,385 --> 00:32:20,501  X1:226 X2:470 Y1:474 Y2:500
You really think he'll tell

373
00:32:20,745 --> 00:32:23,259  X1:207 X2:490 Y1:474 Y2:495
a woman who lives off him?

374
00:32:23,465 --> 00:32:25,342  X1:211 X2:487 Y1:474 Y2:499
Sir, we haven't found much

375
00:32:27,185 --> 00:32:28,334  X1:302 X2:396 Y1:474 Y2:495
That's it?

376
00:32:28,465 --> 00:32:29,784  X1:222 X2:477 Y1:474 Y2:525
We looked through every
drawer and this is it

377
00:32:29,825 --> 00:32:31,577  X1:270 X2:428 Y1:474 Y2:500
Rest is clothing

378
00:32:33,585 --> 00:32:35,098  X1:261 X2:437 Y1:474 Y2:495
How can that be?

379
00:32:35,225 --> 00:32:36,578  X1:173 X2:524 Y1:474 Y2:500
What else do you think there'll be?

380
00:32:36,865 --> 00:32:38,856  X1:234 X2:464 Y1:474 Y2:500
Don't think you've won

381
00:32:39,225 --> 00:32:40,499  X1:293 X2:404 Y1:474 Y2:495
Believe me

382
00:32:40,665 --> 00:32:44,055  X1:280 X2:418 Y1:474 Y2:495
We'll find him

383
00:32:46,305 --> 00:32:48,660  X1:208 X2:490 Y1:474 Y2:500
l've been with Li a long time

384
00:32:48,945 --> 00:32:50,663  X1:235 X2:463 Y1:474 Y2:495
This woman is the one

385
00:32:50,785 --> 00:32:52,423  X1:216 X2:483 Y1:474 Y2:500
he's been with the longest

386
00:32:52,625 --> 00:32:54,104  X1:253 X2:447 Y1:474 Y2:500
Disrespect me now

387
00:32:54,265 --> 00:32:56,176  X1:231 X2:468 Y1:474 Y2:500
and l can finish you off

388
00:32:56,385 --> 00:32:58,853  X1:192 X2:505 Y1:474 Y2:495
with one word when he returns

389
00:33:10,985 --> 00:33:13,863  X1:192 X2:509 Y1:474 Y2:525
Took us two days to line up for
the boat tickets

390
00:33:14,025 --> 00:33:16,903  X1:187 X2:510 Y1:474 Y2:530
Can't imagine how many people
are trying to leave Shanghai

391
00:33:22,185 --> 00:33:25,575  X1:215 X2:484 Y1:474 Y2:530
l thought we were going to
Japan orAmerica

392
00:33:25,745 --> 00:33:26,860  X1:268 X2:430 Y1:474 Y2:500
Neverthought...

393
00:33:27,025 --> 00:33:29,300  X1:137 X2:560 Y1:474 Y2:500
fatherwould finally decide on Hong Kong

394
00:33:37,305 --> 00:33:39,216  X1:238 X2:460 Y1:474 Y2:500
Where is Hong Kong?

395
00:33:39,505 --> 00:33:40,984  X1:289 X2:410 Y1:474 Y2:495
ln the south

396
00:33:41,145 --> 00:33:45,502  X1:175 X2:522 Y1:474 Y2:500
l heard it's a dirty and messy slum

397
00:33:45,825 --> 00:33:47,861  X1:180 X2:517 Y1:474 Y2:500
Yourfatheris a big businessman

398
00:33:48,025 --> 00:33:50,414  X1:243 X2:456 Y1:474 Y2:495
He should know best

399
00:33:51,265 --> 00:33:55,144  X1:162 X2:536 Y1:474 Y2:500
You talk just like my very own Cheng

400
00:33:55,265 --> 00:33:57,415  X1:201 X2:498 Y1:474 Y2:500
Still joking at a time like this?

401
00:33:57,705 --> 00:33:58,933  X1:325 X2:372 Y1:474 Y2:495
Miss

402
00:33:59,105 --> 00:34:00,743  X1:299 X2:399 Y1:474 Y2:495
More tea?

403
00:34:01,225 --> 00:34:03,261  X1:329 X2:368 Y1:474 Y2:495
Yes

404
00:34:13,945 --> 00:34:15,173  X1:319 X2:378 Y1:474 Y2:500
Qiyao

405
00:34:15,905 --> 00:34:18,214  X1:293 X2:405 Y1:474 Y2:495
How's life?

406
00:34:18,625 --> 00:34:21,264  X1:259 X2:438 Y1:474 Y2:500
Everything is fine

407
00:34:21,505 --> 00:34:23,257  X1:285 X2:414 Y1:474 Y2:500
People say...

408
00:34:24,145 --> 00:34:26,613  X1:223 X2:476 Y1:474 Y2:500
Shanghai is too unstable

409
00:34:26,865 --> 00:34:30,141  X1:219 X2:479 Y1:474 Y2:530
lt's best to go some place
for a few years

410
00:34:30,305 --> 00:34:32,341  X1:218 X2:481 Y1:474 Y2:530
Ride it out and come back
when things settle down

411
00:34:32,865 --> 00:34:34,378  X1:299 X2:400 Y1:474 Y2:500
Perhaps...

412
00:34:34,585 --> 00:34:36,894  X1:201 X2:496 Y1:474 Y2:495
You should think about it too

413
00:34:38,105 --> 00:34:39,424  X1:238 X2:461 Y1:474 Y2:500
Leaving just like that?

414
00:34:40,065 --> 00:34:41,498  X1:221 X2:476 Y1:474 Y2:495
lt's easier said than done

415
00:34:45,385 --> 00:34:46,943  X1:319 X2:378 Y1:474 Y2:500
Qiyao

416
00:34:47,345 --> 00:34:48,937  X1:251 X2:447 Y1:474 Y2:500
lt's yourhousehold

417
00:34:49,265 --> 00:34:51,062  X1:214 X2:484 Y1:474 Y2:495
l know l shouldn't interfere

418
00:34:51,545 --> 00:34:53,854  X1:225 X2:474 Y1:474 Y2:500
lt's none of my business

419
00:34:54,865 --> 00:34:56,014  X1:323 X2:376 Y1:474 Y2:495
But...

420
00:34:56,345 --> 00:35:00,657  X1:221 X2:477 Y1:474 Y2:525
That Officer Li can't even
take care of himself now

421
00:35:09,105 --> 00:35:10,060  X1:231 X2:467 Y1:474 Y2:500
There's an old saying...

422
00:35:10,105 --> 00:35:13,654  X1:167 X2:531 Y1:474 Y2:530
Couples are birds in the same wood
that fly off when there's trouble

423
00:35:13,825 --> 00:35:17,420  X1:153 X2:545 Y1:474 Y2:495
This crisis won't end in a month ortwo

424
00:35:18,625 --> 00:35:19,694  X1:310 X2:386 Y1:474 Y2:495
Women

425
00:35:20,345 --> 00:35:23,303  X1:184 X2:515 Y1:474 Y2:495
should think forthemselves first

426
00:35:40,065 --> 00:35:41,214  X1:245 X2:452 Y1:474 Y2:500
You're leaving now?

427
00:35:41,345 --> 00:35:42,937  X1:302 X2:394 Y1:474 Y2:495
Yes Miss

428
00:35:43,265 --> 00:35:44,937  X1:180 X2:521 Y1:474 Y2:500
Please take good care of yourself

429
00:35:45,625 --> 00:35:49,334  X1:136 X2:562 Y1:474 Y2:500
We no longerhave the honorto serve you

430
00:35:49,465 --> 00:35:51,296  X1:279 X2:420 Y1:474 Y2:500
Don't say that

431
00:35:51,505 --> 00:35:54,895  X1:161 X2:537 Y1:474 Y2:500
lt's going to be lonely here by myself

432
00:35:55,025 --> 00:35:56,538  X1:297 X2:401 Y1:474 Y2:495
lt won't be

433
00:35:57,745 --> 00:35:59,383  X1:279 X2:418 Y1:474 Y2:495
You take care

434
00:36:00,185 --> 00:36:03,734  X1:251 X2:447 Y1:474 Y2:500
l will and thank you

435
00:36:31,425 --> 00:36:33,177  X1:258 X2:440 Y1:474 Y2:500
You're MrCheng?

436
00:36:33,665 --> 00:36:35,815  X1:237 X2:461 Y1:474 Y2:500
Sir, your guest is here

437
00:36:35,865 --> 00:36:37,344  X1:307 X2:390 Y1:474 Y2:495
Come in

438
00:36:45,825 --> 00:36:47,019  X1:190 X2:508 Y1:474 Y2:500
Haven't seen you in a long time

439
00:36:47,345 --> 00:36:49,620  X1:295 X2:404 Y1:474 Y2:500
l was busy

440
00:36:53,025 --> 00:36:54,777  X1:239 X2:458 Y1:474 Y2:500
Nice to see you again

441
00:36:59,825 --> 00:37:01,622  X1:243 X2:455 Y1:474 Y2:495
Must be cold outside

442
00:37:01,785 --> 00:37:03,298  X1:315 X2:385 Y1:474 Y2:495
lt's not

443
00:37:11,025 --> 00:37:12,583  X1:279 X2:418 Y1:474 Y2:500
How are you?

444
00:37:15,185 --> 00:37:17,221  X1:327 X2:371 Y1:474 Y2:495
Fine

445
00:37:20,105 --> 00:37:21,743  X1:291 X2:408 Y1:474 Y2:500
Did Qiyao...

446
00:37:21,905 --> 00:37:24,055  X1:277 X2:421 Y1:474 Y2:500
say anything?

447
00:37:24,305 --> 00:37:25,658  X1:335 X2:363 Y1:474 Y2:495
No

448
00:37:28,465 --> 00:37:30,660  X1:233 X2:465 Y1:474 Y2:500
She's still living there?

449
00:37:31,225 --> 00:37:33,534  X1:164 X2:534 Y1:474 Y2:500
We haven't seen each otherrecently

450
00:37:44,545 --> 00:37:46,695  X1:252 X2:446 Y1:474 Y2:500
Could l trouble you

451
00:37:46,865 --> 00:37:48,583  X1:187 X2:510 Y1:474 Y2:500
to make a trip to the apartment?

452
00:37:48,625 --> 00:37:49,978  X1:261 X2:436 Y1:474 Y2:495
lf she's still there

453
00:37:51,705 --> 00:37:53,821  X1:185 X2:513 Y1:474 Y2:500
please deliver a message forme

454
00:37:57,345 --> 00:37:59,939  X1:190 X2:507 Y1:474 Y2:495
You haven't seen herin a while

455
00:38:04,825 --> 00:38:07,293  X1:189 X2:508 Y1:474 Y2:495
Your situation can't be that bad

456
00:38:07,585 --> 00:38:11,464  X1:192 X2:505 Y1:474 Y2:500
Why don't you tell heryourself

457
00:39:06,625 --> 00:39:11,016  X1:156 X2:542 Y1:474 Y2:495
Tell herl'm dead and don't wait forme

458
00:39:11,945 --> 00:39:14,459  X1:232 X2:469 Y1:474 Y2:500
How dare you lie to her

459
00:39:17,225 --> 00:39:19,693  X1:258 X2:441 Y1:474 Y2:500
You can run away

460
00:39:19,865 --> 00:39:21,856  X1:182 X2:516 Y1:474 Y2:500
But what is she supposed to do?

461
00:39:23,505 --> 00:39:25,735  X1:263 X2:435 Y1:474 Y2:500
lf l see a way out

462
00:39:25,905 --> 00:39:28,055  X1:190 X2:508 Y1:474 Y2:500
Do you think l'll be asking you?

463
00:40:07,825 --> 00:40:09,019  X1:222 X2:476 Y1:474 Y2:500
Aren't you having some?

464
00:40:10,945 --> 00:40:12,424  X1:279 X2:419 Y1:474 Y2:500
l'm not thirsty

465
00:40:28,905 --> 00:40:31,055  X1:256 X2:444 Y1:474 Y2:500
Lili left yesterday?

466
00:40:35,545 --> 00:40:39,060  X1:194 X2:505 Y1:474 Y2:500
l should've gone to see her off

467
00:40:43,185 --> 00:40:46,097  X1:136 X2:561 Y1:474 Y2:500
You shouldn't be worrying about this now

468
00:40:48,265 --> 00:40:50,654  X1:312 X2:386 Y1:474 Y2:495
l'm fine

469
00:40:51,945 --> 00:40:54,857  X1:184 X2:514 Y1:474 Y2:500
l'll stay here for a few more days

470
00:41:19,905 --> 00:41:22,897  X1:171 X2:527 Y1:474 Y2:500
Get changed and l'll take you home

471
00:41:27,825 --> 00:41:29,463  X1:252 X2:445 Y1:474 Y2:500
We're good friends

472
00:41:33,345 --> 00:41:35,984  X1:197 X2:500 Y1:474 Y2:530
He was gone just like that...
How can you be heartbroken?

473
00:41:36,145 --> 00:41:37,658  X1:239 X2:459 Y1:474 Y2:495
He's dead! He's dead!

474
00:41:37,785 --> 00:41:41,221  X1:167 X2:532 Y1:474 Y2:500
He was thinking of me when he died

475
00:41:44,625 --> 00:41:47,697  X1:199 X2:498 Y1:474 Y2:500
Forhim...l can give up my life

476
00:41:47,745 --> 00:41:50,817  X1:203 X2:494 Y1:474 Y2:500
And you all think l don't care

477
00:41:51,825 --> 00:41:53,975  X1:237 X2:461 Y1:474 Y2:500
He made me lie to you

478
00:41:54,265 --> 00:41:56,221  X1:269 X2:429 Y1:474 Y2:495
He'll come back

479
00:42:17,625 --> 00:42:21,823  X1:138 X2:560 Y1:474 Y2:530
Qiyao believed loving someone was more
important than anything in life

480
00:42:22,105 --> 00:42:26,178  X1:222 X2:476 Y1:474 Y2:530
Yet my wife believed
we should love everyone

481
00:42:26,945 --> 00:42:30,255  X1:227 X2:471 Y1:474 Y2:530
That was what l heard
from the radio everyday

482
00:42:30,985 --> 00:42:33,943  X1:219 X2:479 Y1:474 Y2:530
And l was beginning to
believe what my wife said

483
00:42:34,745 --> 00:42:36,337  X1:275 X2:425 Y1:474 Y2:495
Do it tomorrow

484
00:42:39,145 --> 00:42:43,184  X1:227 X2:470 Y1:474 Y2:530
Aren't you tired working
so late every night?

485
00:42:43,465 --> 00:42:47,936  X1:211 X2:488 Y1:474 Y2:530
l can't sleep well
if l left any work unfinished

486
00:42:53,985 --> 00:42:56,818  X1:196 X2:502 Y1:474 Y2:500
Hasn't snowed for a few years

487
00:43:02,625 --> 00:43:04,820  X1:211 X2:489 Y1:474 Y2:500
Don't just stare at the snow

488
00:43:04,945 --> 00:43:07,413  X1:181 X2:517 Y1:474 Y2:500
Do you have enough clothes on?

489
00:43:11,185 --> 00:43:12,857  X1:329 X2:368 Y1:474 Y2:495
Yes

490
00:43:12,905 --> 00:43:15,294  X1:289 X2:409 Y1:474 Y2:500
That's good

491
00:43:18,425 --> 00:43:21,861  X1:250 X2:451 Y1:474 Y2:500
Let's go out and eat

492
00:43:41,785 --> 00:43:43,264  X1:296 X2:402 Y1:474 Y2:500
Thank you

493
00:43:49,305 --> 00:43:51,057  X1:216 X2:483 Y1:474 Y2:500
The songs of a New China

494
00:43:51,505 --> 00:43:53,655  X1:209 X2:489 Y1:474 Y2:525
Gave people the courage to
make brave new decisions

495
00:44:10,825 --> 00:44:12,941  X1:294 X2:404 Y1:474 Y2:500
Miss Wang

496
00:44:15,745 --> 00:44:18,657  X1:234 X2:464 Y1:474 Y2:495
Please come overhere

497
00:44:24,385 --> 00:44:26,057  X1:150 X2:548 Y1:474 Y2:500
Thank you foryourhonorable donation

498
00:44:26,225 --> 00:44:27,499  X1:189 X2:511 Y1:474 Y2:500
of this apartment to the country

499
00:44:27,625 --> 00:44:31,504  X1:252 X2:448 Y1:474 Y2:499
Please, have a seat

500
00:44:34,385 --> 00:44:36,501  X1:266 X2:434 Y1:474 Y2:500
Please sign here

501
00:45:34,985 --> 00:45:38,625  X1:193 X2:505 Y1:474 Y2:530
lf it's our country that needs it,
l've nothing against it

502
00:45:38,625 --> 00:45:42,061  X1:185 X2:514 Y1:474 Y2:500
Donate your stock holdings now

503
00:45:42,305 --> 00:45:45,422  X1:226 X2:473 Y1:474 Y2:500
to benefit the proletariat

504
00:45:45,585 --> 00:45:48,338  X1:190 X2:506 Y1:474 Y2:500
When our country is stronger...

505
00:45:48,625 --> 00:45:50,900  X1:285 X2:412 Y1:474 Y2:495
What's that?

506
00:45:51,025 --> 00:45:53,778  X1:215 X2:486 Y1:474 Y2:500
Documents foryourfather

507
00:46:08,225 --> 00:46:09,180  X1:287 X2:410 Y1:474 Y2:500
MasterMing

508
00:46:11,105 --> 00:46:12,504  X1:287 X2:410 Y1:474 Y2:500
MasterMing

509
00:46:13,985 --> 00:46:15,703  X1:210 X2:488 Y1:474 Y2:500
You're packing up already?

510
00:46:15,825 --> 00:46:17,258  X1:168 X2:529 Y1:474 Y2:500
You haven't had yourinjection yet?

511
00:46:17,305 --> 00:46:17,862  X1:287 X2:410 Y1:474 Y2:500
MasterMing

512
00:46:19,025 --> 00:46:19,537  X1:321 X2:377 Y1:474 Y2:500
Sorry

513
00:46:20,425 --> 00:46:22,745  X1:232 X2:466 Y1:474 Y2:500
You're packing already

514
00:46:22,745 --> 00:46:23,416  X1:287 X2:415 Y1:474 Y2:495
Don't bother

515
00:46:23,585 --> 00:46:24,938  X1:223 X2:476 Y1:474 Y2:500
MasterMing, you go first

516
00:46:25,385 --> 00:46:28,218  X1:223 X2:477 Y1:474 Y2:500
l'm not busy, you go first

517
00:47:23,385 --> 00:47:25,103  X1:202 X2:496 Y1:474 Y2:500
What will people think of us?

518
00:47:28,825 --> 00:47:31,180  X1:231 X2:468 Y1:474 Y2:500
l won't ask for anything

519
00:47:34,105 --> 00:47:35,663  X1:326 X2:372 Y1:474 Y2:495
l will

520
00:47:37,145 --> 00:47:38,180  X1:321 X2:379 Y1:474 Y2:500
Say it

521
00:47:41,705 --> 00:47:42,854  X1:289 X2:408 Y1:474 Y2:495
Think of me

522
00:47:43,585 --> 00:47:44,540  X1:204 X2:493 Y1:474 Y2:500
when you feel sad, will you?

523
00:47:58,505 --> 00:48:00,257  X1:280 X2:417 Y1:474 Y2:500
Ask me again

524
00:48:00,505 --> 00:48:02,223  X1:275 X2:423 Y1:474 Y2:500
during the day

525
00:48:06,025 --> 00:48:09,062  X1:255 X2:444 Y1:474 Y2:500
l won't say it again

526
00:48:09,665 --> 00:48:11,496  X1:202 X2:496 Y1:474 Y2:500
What is said during the night

527
00:48:12,425 --> 00:48:13,335  X1:279 X2:419 Y1:474 Y2:495
doesn't count

528
00:48:18,335 --> 00:48:20,485  X1:228 X2:469 Y1:474 Y2:495
What will become of me

529
00:48:22,175 --> 00:48:23,130  X1:226 X2:472 Y1:474 Y2:500
if l can't make you stay?

530
00:48:30,255 --> 00:48:32,132  X1:233 X2:466 Y1:474 Y2:500
l'm trying to work it out

531
00:48:40,335 --> 00:48:42,166  X1:337 X2:361 Y1:474 Y2:495
l...

532
00:48:42,775 --> 00:48:44,413  X1:259 X2:441 Y1:474 Y2:500
have nothing now

533
00:48:50,735 --> 00:48:52,487  X1:234 X2:465 Y1:474 Y2:500
We finally went too far

534
00:48:53,575 --> 00:48:54,849  X1:320 X2:378 Y1:474 Y2:500
Why?

535
00:48:57,655 --> 00:48:59,930  X1:234 X2:464 Y1:474 Y2:500
You irresponsible man

536
00:49:00,335 --> 00:49:02,803  X1:237 X2:460 Y1:474 Y2:500
The father of my child

537
00:49:04,655 --> 00:49:06,327  X1:185 X2:512 Y1:474 Y2:500
