01:03:01,415 --> 01:03:03,246  X1:218 X2:483 Y1:474 Y2:500
Little Weiwei, look at Papa

717
01:03:16,175 --> 01:03:17,608  X1:272 X2:427 Y1:474 Y2:500
Dinneris ready

718
01:03:26,815 --> 01:03:29,932  X1:161 X2:538 Y1:474 Y2:500
Chicken soup is good foryourhealth

719
01:03:41,015 --> 01:03:42,971  X1:238 X2:461 Y1:474 Y2:500
l'll take care of myself

720
01:03:50,095 --> 01:03:52,211  X1:223 X2:474 Y1:474 Y2:495
Does she drink hermilk?

721
01:03:52,335 --> 01:03:53,529  X1:255 X2:443 Y1:474 Y2:500
She's a good child

722
01:03:53,695 --> 01:03:55,333  X1:169 X2:528 Y1:474 Y2:500
Drinks hermilk with all her strength

723
01:03:55,495 --> 01:03:57,292  X1:216 X2:481 Y1:474 Y2:500
And then go right to sleep

724
01:03:58,415 --> 01:03:59,768  X1:295 X2:405 Y1:474 Y2:495
How sweet

725
01:03:59,935 --> 01:04:01,607  X1:329 X2:368 Y1:474 Y2:495
Yes

726
01:04:01,855 --> 01:04:03,652  X1:191 X2:510 Y1:474 Y2:500
l neverhave to worry about her

727
01:04:05,055 --> 01:04:06,613  X1:289 X2:409 Y1:474 Y2:500
That's good

728
01:04:17,655 --> 01:04:20,408  X1:219 X2:479 Y1:474 Y2:525
Every man wants a family
he can call his own

729
01:04:21,815 --> 01:04:24,124  X1:226 X2:471 Y1:474 Y2:495
With a wife and children

730
01:04:25,375 --> 01:04:27,331  X1:184 X2:514 Y1:474 Y2:500
Living a steady and peaceful life

731
01:04:31,215 --> 01:04:33,934  X1:168 X2:530 Y1:474 Y2:530
l grew up watching
my uncles' families and l envy them

732
01:04:34,175 --> 01:04:36,006  X1:293 X2:407 Y1:474 Y2:500
in my heart

733
01:04:37,335 --> 01:04:39,166  X1:183 X2:517 Y1:474 Y2:500
lt makes me want to grow up fast

734
01:04:40,335 --> 01:04:41,848  X1:221 X2:476 Y1:474 Y2:495
So that l can be like them

735
01:04:42,775 --> 01:04:44,447  X1:204 X2:493 Y1:474 Y2:500
And introduce to everyone...

736
01:04:45,135 --> 01:04:46,614  X1:311 X2:388 Y1:474 Y2:500
My wife

737
01:04:46,895 --> 01:04:48,248  X1:313 X2:386 Y1:474 Y2:500
My son

738
01:04:48,895 --> 01:04:49,930  X1:261 X2:439 Y1:474 Y2:500
And my daughter

739
01:04:53,535 --> 01:04:54,888  X1:295 X2:404 Y1:474 Y2:500
l thought...

740
01:04:55,015 --> 01:04:58,371  X1:155 X2:538 Y1:474 Y2:530
So what if we don't go to Hong Kong?
We can stay in Shanghai

741
01:04:58,535 --> 01:05:00,651  X1:191 X2:508 Y1:474 Y2:500
But that doesn't solve anything

742
01:05:07,135 --> 01:05:10,605  X1:171 X2:528 Y1:474 Y2:530
No use thinking about it anymore...
lf my motherwere still here

743
01:05:10,695 --> 01:05:15,132  X1:192 X2:506 Y1:474 Y2:530
She could at least get a golden
bracelet from her grandma

744
01:05:15,295 --> 01:05:17,251  X1:229 X2:470 Y1:474 Y2:495
Such a sweet little child

745
01:05:17,655 --> 01:05:20,613  X1:199 X2:498 Y1:474 Y2:495
Born into this cold loneliness

746
01:05:22,095 --> 01:05:25,007  X1:150 X2:548 Y1:474 Y2:500
Don't worry about yourliving expenses

747
01:05:25,535 --> 01:05:27,765  X1:203 X2:494 Y1:474 Y2:530
Even when l'm in Hong Kong
and not by your side

748
01:05:28,135 --> 01:05:31,093  X1:229 X2:470 Y1:474 Y2:500
l'll still send you money

749
01:05:38,055 --> 01:05:41,047  X1:209 X2:491 Y1:474 Y2:500
l'm counting on you forthat

750
01:05:42,135 --> 01:05:43,284  X1:317 X2:383 Y1:474 Y2:495
l know

751
01:05:47,175 --> 01:05:49,735  X1:283 X2:417 Y1:474 Y2:499
Come on, eat

752
01:05:49,855 --> 01:05:51,254  X1:228 X2:470 Y1:474 Y2:500
The food is getting cold

753
01:05:52,615 --> 01:05:56,972  X1:163 X2:536 Y1:474 Y2:500
Ming died in San Francisco at age 59

754
01:06:02,925 --> 01:06:06,122  X1:231 X2:466 Y1:474 Y2:500
My wife kept asking me

755
01:06:06,565 --> 01:06:09,033  X1:180 X2:520 Y1:474 Y2:500
why Qiyao didn't come for dinner

756
01:06:09,605 --> 01:06:12,995  X1:191 X2:506 Y1:474 Y2:500
l guess she felt sorry forQiyao

757
01:06:14,965 --> 01:06:17,399  X1:174 X2:524 Y1:474 Y2:500
But l understood Qiyao all too well

758
01:06:17,645 --> 01:06:21,718  X1:194 X2:505 Y1:474 Y2:525
When she was sad she did not
want to be disturbed

759
01:06:39,005 --> 01:06:40,882  X1:189 X2:510 Y1:474 Y2:500
l don't want to pretend anymore

760
01:06:41,245 --> 01:06:42,963  X1:239 X2:461 Y1:474 Y2:500
lf you can't forget her

761
01:06:43,125 --> 01:06:45,480  X1:242 X2:459 Y1:474 Y2:495
l'll make room forher

762
01:06:50,605 --> 01:06:54,154  X1:165 X2:534 Y1:474 Y2:500
l'm someone who can find a way out

763
01:07:10,365 --> 01:07:12,083  X1:229 X2:470 Y1:474 Y2:500
How was school today?

764
01:07:12,205 --> 01:07:13,194  X1:321 X2:376 Y1:474 Y2:495
Good

765
01:07:13,645 --> 01:07:15,715  X1:192 X2:504 Y1:474 Y2:500
Want egg fried rice for dinner?.

766
01:07:15,805 --> 01:07:16,635  X1:329 X2:368 Y1:474 Y2:495
Yes

767
01:07:16,725 --> 01:07:17,919  X1:298 X2:401 Y1:474 Y2:495
Tell Mama

768
01:07:18,885 --> 01:07:20,876  X1:125 X2:573 Y1:474 Y2:500
How much are the eggs in the black market?

769
01:07:21,005 --> 01:07:22,358  X1:272 X2:426 Y1:474 Y2:495
Does it matter?.

770
01:07:22,565 --> 01:07:24,476  X1:203 X2:496 Y1:474 Y2:500
l'll get them if you need them

771
01:07:24,565 --> 01:07:27,716  X1:172 X2:526 Y1:474 Y2:530
Ma, wheneverUncle Cheng comes,
we have egg fried rice

772
01:07:27,845 --> 01:07:29,517  X1:220 X2:478 Y1:474 Y2:500
Let Uncle Cheng kiss you

773
01:07:31,805 --> 01:07:33,397  X1:274 X2:426 Y1:474 Y2:500
Run along now

774
01:07:35,605 --> 01:07:38,073  X1:242 X2:456 Y1:474 Y2:500
Qiyao, the egg shells

775
01:07:38,205 --> 01:07:40,161  X1:199 X2:501 Y1:474 Y2:500
l'll dispose them outside later

776
01:07:40,645 --> 01:07:43,364  X1:151 X2:546 Y1:474 Y2:495
Can't be careless with the small details

777
01:07:44,485 --> 01:07:47,363  X1:184 X2:513 Y1:474 Y2:530
That family out
front is always turning people in

778
01:07:47,405 --> 01:07:49,077  X1:234 X2:463 Y1:474 Y2:500
With so many enemies

779
01:07:49,125 --> 01:07:51,685  X1:201 X2:501 Y1:474 Y2:525
One of these days,
someone will return the favor

780
01:07:51,805 --> 01:07:54,877  X1:169 X2:528 Y1:474 Y2:530
Don't mind otherpeople's business
and just take care of yourself

781
01:08:03,525 --> 01:08:06,642  X1:241 X2:456 Y1:474 Y2:530
Going to rural areas
to help those in need

782
01:08:07,005 --> 01:08:10,156  X1:271 X2:427 Y1:474 Y2:495
l believe in that

783
01:08:10,565 --> 01:08:12,760  X1:196 X2:501 Y1:474 Y2:500
When l said goodbye to Qiyao

784
01:08:12,925 --> 01:08:15,200  X1:166 X2:533 Y1:474 Y2:500
She asked me to take care of myself

785
01:08:16,485 --> 01:08:18,919  X1:212 X2:485 Y1:474 Y2:525
And l told herto
take care of herself as well

786
01:08:29,365 --> 01:08:35,201  X1:184 X2:516 Y1:474 Y2:530
Great as are heaven and earth,
what we owe the Party is greater

787
01:08:36,005 --> 01:08:41,523  X1:198 X2:503 Y1:474 Y2:525
Dear as are father and mother
Chairman Mao is dearer

788
01:08:41,885 --> 01:08:43,716  X1:202 X2:496 Y1:474 Y2:500
Ma, l'll teach you how to sing

789
01:08:43,805 --> 01:08:44,954  X1:323 X2:375 Y1:474 Y2:500
Okay

790
01:08:52,045 --> 01:08:53,717  X1:217 X2:482 Y1:474 Y2:500
Chairman Mao taught us...

791
01:08:53,805 --> 01:08:55,033  X1:255 X2:443 Y1:474 Y2:500
The world is yours

792
01:08:55,205 --> 01:08:56,479  X1:270 X2:426 Y1:474 Y2:495
As well as ours

793
01:08:56,565 --> 01:08:58,840  X1:225 X2:472 Y1:474 Y2:500
But ultimately it is yours

794
01:09:12,765 --> 01:09:14,596  X1:285 X2:413 Y1:474 Y2:495
lt works now

795
01:09:15,045 --> 01:09:17,195  X1:198 X2:500 Y1:474 Y2:530
Kela, where did you find this?
Don't let anyone find out

796
01:09:17,285 --> 01:09:18,957  X1:205 X2:492 Y1:474 Y2:500
Of course not...lt's very safe

797
01:09:29,685 --> 01:09:31,198  X1:282 X2:416 Y1:474 Y2:500
Working yet?

798
01:09:33,885 --> 01:09:35,079  X1:201 X2:496 Y1:474 Y2:495
How come there's no sound?

799
01:09:40,285 --> 01:09:41,718  X1:298 X2:400 Y1:474 Y2:495
No needle

800
01:09:41,845 --> 01:09:44,359  X1:167 X2:532 Y1:474 Y2:500
Cousin, see if you can find a needle

801
01:09:44,405 --> 01:09:45,360  X1:279 X2:418 Y1:474 Y2:495
What needle?

802
01:09:45,445 --> 01:09:47,356  X1:229 X2:468 Y1:474 Y2:530
How can we find record
playing needles here?

803
01:09:49,245 --> 01:09:51,076  X1:251 X2:449 Y1:474 Y2:500
l've been ripped off

804
01:09:51,165 --> 01:09:52,917  X1:228 X2:471 Y1:474 Y2:500
l gave him a watch forit

805
01:09:53,005 --> 01:09:54,154  X1:241 X2:456 Y1:474 Y2:500
What did he tell you?

806
01:09:54,205 --> 01:09:55,797  X1:209 X2:490 Y1:474 Y2:500
He guaranteed it would turn

807
01:09:56,765 --> 01:09:57,993  X1:300 X2:398 Y1:474 Y2:495
No sound

808
01:09:58,405 --> 01:09:59,679  X1:307 X2:393 Y1:474 Y2:500
Forget it

809
01:10:17,805 --> 01:10:19,523  X1:257 X2:441 Y1:474 Y2:500
Cheng, take a rest

810
01:10:25,845 --> 01:10:26,595  X1:316 X2:382 Y1:474 Y2:500
Cheng

811
01:10:28,765 --> 01:10:31,325  X1:240 X2:458 Y1:474 Y2:500
Stop working like this

812
01:10:32,645 --> 01:10:35,682  X1:177 X2:523 Y1:474 Y2:500
Look at you, doing nothing all day

813
01:10:37,405 --> 01:10:38,201  X1:313 X2:385 Y1:474 Y2:495
Cousin

814
01:10:38,445 --> 01:10:40,401  X1:193 X2:509 Y1:474 Y2:495
Don't disturb ourmodel worker

815
01:10:40,605 --> 01:10:42,994  X1:222 X2:477 Y1:474 Y2:530
Kela, why are you always
protecting him?

816
01:10:44,525 --> 01:10:45,480  X1:303 X2:396 Y1:474 Y2:495
Don't run

817
01:10:48,365 --> 01:10:50,003  X1:270 X2:428 Y1:474 Y2:500
Cheng, help me

818
01:10:54,605 --> 01:10:56,436  X1:270 X2:428 Y1:474 Y2:500
Cheng, help me

819
01:10:56,525 --> 01:10:59,039  X1:191 X2:506 Y1:474 Y2:500
l'll write to Aunt and tell on you

820
01:10:59,645 --> 01:11:01,317  X1:208 X2:490 Y1:474 Y2:499
Go ahead, see if l'm worried

821
01:11:03,965 --> 01:11:05,193  X1:286 X2:412 Y1:474 Y2:500
Let go of me

822
01:11:07,045 --> 01:11:08,160  X1:316 X2:382 Y1:474 Y2:500
Cheng

823
01:11:09,565 --> 01:11:11,237  X1:246 X2:451 Y1:474 Y2:500
Watch what you say

824
01:11:11,365 --> 01:11:13,435  X1:239 X2:461 Y1:474 Y2:500
Don't worry about her

825
01:11:14,005 --> 01:11:15,199  X1:286 X2:411 Y1:474 Y2:500
And you too

826
01:11:25,085 --> 01:11:27,076  X1:177 X2:520 Y1:474 Y2:500
Cheng, do you think about home?

827
01:11:27,325 --> 01:11:28,394  X1:330 X2:368 Y1:474 Y2:495
l do

828
01:11:28,525 --> 01:11:30,243  X1:236 X2:462 Y1:474 Y2:530
l wish l could go back
to Shanghai tomorrow

829
01:11:38,325 --> 01:11:39,678  X1:214 X2:484 Y1:474 Y2:500
Must be nice having a wife

830
01:11:39,725 --> 01:11:40,840  X1:295 X2:402 Y1:474 Y2:500
lt depends

831
01:11:40,925 --> 01:11:42,517  X1:233 X2:465 Y1:474 Y2:495
Not if she's not around

832
01:11:43,405 --> 01:11:44,838  X1:217 X2:480 Y1:474 Y2:500
lt's the same for everyone

833
01:11:45,485 --> 01:11:48,158  X1:234 X2:465 Y1:474 Y2:500
My husband is in Tibet

834
01:11:48,245 --> 01:11:50,805  X1:197 X2:502 Y1:474 Y2:500
Cheng, is yourwife beautiful?

835
01:11:54,005 --> 01:11:55,040  X1:277 X2:420 Y1:474 Y2:500
Very beautiful

836
01:12:07,125 --> 01:12:11,243  X1:203 X2:494 Y1:474 Y2:525
Everyday in the countryside,
l wanted to write a letter

837
01:12:12,485 --> 01:12:16,956  X1:201 X2:497 Y1:474 Y2:530
To know what my friend's life
was like in Shanghai

838
01:12:17,485 --> 01:12:19,555  X1:155 X2:543 Y1:474 Y2:500
l had to think about every word l wrote

839
01:12:21,045 --> 01:12:24,117  X1:147 X2:550 Y1:474 Y2:500
For one wrong word could bring trouble

840
01:12:24,285 --> 01:12:27,960  X1:175 X2:525 Y1:474 Y2:500
l ended up only sending one letter

841
01:12:28,965 --> 01:12:32,241  X1:241 X2:457 Y1:474 Y2:530
On it, l drew a picture
of a young Qiyao

842
01:12:32,965 --> 01:12:36,514  X1:187 X2:510 Y1:474 Y2:500
She should know l was asking...

843
01:12:36,845 --> 01:12:38,278  X1:279 X2:418 Y1:474 Y2:500
How are you?

844
01:12:39,125 --> 01:12:40,399  X1:268 X2:430 Y1:474 Y2:500
Are you happy?

845
01:12:41,125 --> 01:12:45,755  X1:176 X2:524 Y1:474 Y2:500
Ayearpassed... and then another

846
01:12:45,845 --> 01:12:50,794  X1:205 X2:493 Y1:474 Y2:525
people gradually returned to
their own cities

847
01:12:53,485 --> 01:12:54,679  X1:239 X2:458 Y1:474 Y2:500
Comrade, how many?

848
01:12:54,965 --> 01:12:56,683  X1:227 X2:471 Y1:474 Y2:500
l'm looking for someone

849
01:13:16,285 --> 01:13:19,800  X1:191 X2:506 Y1:474 Y2:530
l burnt the letters from you and
Ming afterreading them

850
01:13:19,885 --> 01:13:21,477  X1:221 X2:477 Y1:474 Y2:500
l didn't dare to keep them

851
01:13:22,565 --> 01:13:24,476  X1:191 X2:506 Y1:474 Y2:500
The few times you sent me rice

852
01:13:25,685 --> 01:13:26,913  X1:263 X2:434 Y1:474 Y2:500
lt tasted so good

853
01:13:27,565 --> 01:13:28,918  X1:245 X2:452 Y1:474 Y2:495
And smelled so nice

854
01:13:30,285 --> 01:13:33,482  X1:199 X2:500 Y1:474 Y2:500
Ming didn't send money twice

855
01:13:34,485 --> 01:13:36,077  X1:231 X2:467 Y1:474 Y2:495
Turned out he was sick

856
01:13:37,765 --> 01:13:39,562  X1:168 X2:528 Y1:474 Y2:500
Amazing how a strong man like him

857
01:13:40,125 --> 01:13:41,922  X1:251 X2:448 Y1:474 Y2:500
can fall ill so easily

858
01:13:46,685 --> 01:13:48,994  X1:166 X2:533 Y1:474 Y2:500
Weiwei tries hard to improve herself

859
01:13:49,925 --> 01:13:53,076  X1:137 X2:562 Y1:474 Y2:500
She asks me to teach herEnglish at home

860
01:13:53,205 --> 01:13:58,199  X1:162 X2:536 Y1:474 Y2:500
But pretends not to know it in school

861
01:14:22,405 --> 01:14:25,442  X1:175 X2:522 Y1:474 Y2:530
Need help to clean up yourplace?
l'll come by tomorrow

862
01:14:25,525 --> 01:14:27,004  X1:253 X2:446 Y1:474 Y2:500
l cleaned it already

863
01:14:30,325 --> 01:14:31,883  X1:245 X2:453 Y1:474 Y2:500
lt's been a few years

864
01:14:33,165 --> 01:14:34,678  X1:274 X2:425 Y1:474 Y2:495
You look older

865
01:14:55,565 --> 01:14:56,680  X1:305 X2:393 Y1:474 Y2:500
lt's good

866
01:15:01,005 --> 01:15:02,154  X1:291 X2:409 Y1:474 Y2:495
To be older

867
01:15:12,925 --> 01:15:14,643  X1:201 X2:498 Y1:474 Y2:500
Neverthought it'd be like this

868
01:16:03,925 --> 01:16:05,517  X1:199 X2:498 Y1:474 Y2:500
Yonghong, have some coffee

869
01:16:05,605 --> 01:16:06,879  X1:225 X2:472 Y1:474 Y2:500
Thank you, Auntie Wang

870
01:16:09,245 --> 01:16:13,523  X1:203 X2:499 Y1:474 Y2:530
Ma, the coffee is bitter...
lt needs more milk and sugar

871
01:16:13,645 --> 01:16:16,364  X1:179 X2:520 Y1:474 Y2:495
lt's not coffee when it's too sweet

872
01:16:17,405 --> 01:16:20,920  X1:240 X2:457 Y1:474 Y2:530
Was it hard to get the
telephone installed?

873
01:16:21,405 --> 01:16:24,397  X1:151 X2:548 Y1:474 Y2:500
Had to go through several departments

874
01:16:24,845 --> 01:16:27,234  X1:214 X2:484 Y1:474 Y2:500
How much did you spend?

875
01:16:28,925 --> 01:16:31,439  X1:184 X2:514 Y1:474 Y2:530
Can we use yourphone for
organizing parties from now on?

876
01:16:34,045 --> 01:16:36,605  X1:199 X2:500 Y1:474 Y2:500
Most people share one phone

877
01:16:36,685 --> 01:16:38,721  X1:143 X2:557 Y1:474 Y2:500
among several buildings and they get by

878
01:16:38,805 --> 01:16:40,363  X1:179 X2:519 Y1:474 Y2:500
Weiwei, you got married too early

879
01:16:40,445 --> 01:16:42,640  X1:201 X2:497 Y1:474 Y2:500
House parties are a lot of fun

880
01:16:43,805 --> 01:16:47,195  X1:156 X2:542 Y1:474 Y2:530
l need to cook when l get off work and
my husband is busy learning English

881
01:16:47,285 --> 01:16:49,003  X1:210 X2:489 Y1:474 Y2:495
l've to do all the housework

882
01:16:49,045 --> 01:16:50,637  X1:190 X2:508 Y1:474 Y2:500
How can l find time forparties?

883
01:16:51,205 --> 01:16:53,514  X1:210 X2:487 Y1:474 Y2:530
Why do you have to stay at
that tiny place

884
01:16:53,645 --> 01:16:55,920  X1:205 X2:492 Y1:474 Y2:500
and do everything yourself?

885
01:16:56,165 --> 01:16:57,678  X1:264 X2:434 Y1:474 Y2:495
l have room here

886
01:16:57,765 --> 01:17:01,201  X1:239 X2:458 Y1:474 Y2:530
l've said it before and
l won't say it again

887
01:17:02,765 --> 01:17:04,881  X1:193 X2:504 Y1:474 Y2:500
Auntie, may l use yourphone?

888
01:17:12,845 --> 01:17:15,643  X1:263 X2:434 Y1:474 Y2:500
How is yourlife?

889
01:17:18,605 --> 01:17:20,561  X1:250 X2:448 Y1:474 Y2:499
Same old, same old

890
01:17:21,365 --> 01:17:23,560  X1:134 X2:566 Y1:474 Y2:500
Living in Shanghai is meaningless anyway

